{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"24":{"eng-name":"Wages (Kitab Al-Ijarah)","ara-name":"كتاب الإجارة"}},"section_detail":{"24":{"hadithnumber_first":3416,"hadithnumber_last":3570,"arabicnumber_first":3416,"arabicnumber_last":3570}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3472,"arabicnumber":3472,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا سُلَيْمَانُ بْنُ دَاوُدَ، أَخْبَرَنَا ابْنُ وَهْبٍ، أَخْبَرَنِي عُثْمَانُ بْنُ الْحَكَمِ، عَنْ يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ، أَنَّهُ قَالَ لاَ جَائِحَةَ فِيمَا أُصِيبَ دُونَ ثُلُثِ رَأْسِ الْمَالِ - قَالَ يَحْيَى - وَذَلِكَ فِي سُنَّةِ الْمُسْلِمِينَ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Maqtu"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Maqtu"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Maqtu"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":24,"hadith":57},"chapter":{"id":25,"ara-name":"باب فِي تَفْسِيرِ الْجَائِحَةِ","eng-name":"Regarding The Explanation Of Blight","isFirstHadith":false}}]}